Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセ）\Nついに 魔法使いと決別した少女
Dialogue: 5,0:23:58.71,0:24:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She follows Joseph down into\Nthe nightmare that torments her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少女はヨセフの導くままに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己を責め苛(さいな)む悪夢へと落ちていく
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（チセの母）許して…
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.80,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Chise.
